*Umesto* da se čovek popravi, on samo pogoršava stvari. (Instead of improving, he just makes things worse.)

*Umesto* da ide u školu, dete je ostalo kod kuće. (Instead of going to school, the child stayed home.)

*Umestom* da čeka, ona je odlučila da napravi promenu. (Instead of waiting, she decided to make a change.)

*Umesto* da bude zahvalna, ona je pokazala ogorčenje. (Instead of being grateful, she showed resentment.)

*Umesto* da greši, on je pravilno uradio posao. (Instead of making mistakes, he did the job correctly.)